reviewText: Really bad acting here; not a turn on !
Kymberly Jane is outstanding!  It's worth the price just to see her perform.  I would give the video five stars if there were more scenes with her.

I usually pick up the DVD's from this company and the ones released by Candygirl Video. I always find them entertaining and Erotic. I would call it a step up from soft-core. They typically do solo girl videos. The surprise in this one was a scene with Jeska Vardinski. She's a popular tattooed model that does not do this type of video. She even mentioned during an interview on this DVD. As usual with their videos. they has bonus scenes and Q&A sessions with the models.
